WITH new_session AS (
                INSERT INTO session
                    (
                     cookie_value,
                     user_id,
                     expiration
                ) VALUES ($1, $2, now() + '1 month')
                RETURNING *)
            SELECT cookie_value,
                   u.id AS user_id,
                   roles,
                   status AS "status: MembershipStatus",
                   expiration
            FROM new_session
                JOIN "user" u ON user_id = u.id
